text:
Fue...
Ah, my legs are trembling~

Mamimi, Yuika~,
Am I standing up well~?

Compared to crawling earlier,
I might be doing a little better-

I'm standing up~!
If it seems okay, I'll relax my muscles a bit more!

I'm trying to relax my muscles...
But it feels like I'm slipping in a weird direction, I-I can't...!

Ugh... I fell over...
It's okay, I'm not injured or anything...

But well,
I think I'm starting to get the hang of it...

I'll be able to slide smoothly in no time~!
Leave it to me~!!
